Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:02.23,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}We've been around the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.98,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Carry each other to hell and back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:10.66,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Into a brand new dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:14.83,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Burning our bridges with the past
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:18.79,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}And where you lead sister, I will follow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:22.96,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}From the shadows of the past to the shimmers of tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:32.59,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}For the bond we share is beyond compare, it's unbreakable
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:37.81,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}'Cause this is the moment we're waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:45.57,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}And this is the day we spread our wings and fly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:52.24,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Nothing can break this army of two
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:54.83,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Ain't nothing gonna stop us, girl
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:59.91,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}It's you, you, you and I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:17.60,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Army of two
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:26.52,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Army of two
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:34.78,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Army of two
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:02.23,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}我们围绕着太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.98,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}互相支撑着从地狱返回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:10.66,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}向着新的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:14.83,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}与过去诀别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:18.79,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}如果你指明方向  我便会紧紧跟随
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:22.96,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}走出过去的阴影  向着明日的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:32.59,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}我们之间的纽带无论如何都不会断裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:37.81,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}这一刻我们期待良久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:45.57,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}这一天我们展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:52.24,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}没有什么能打败我们两人的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:54.83,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}没有什么能阻止你我前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:59.91,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}是你  是你  是你  和我的前进
