Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.05,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}I was young not too long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.30,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}Took a little time to see it clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:34.31,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}Clearly you are not my pot o' gold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.02,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}Everything was cool without you & me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:44.07,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}But I'm not afraid of love no more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:49.12,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}I know it's dangerous, for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:54.12,EDEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}But somehow I'm craving love once more
